{"tid":626706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲男病人擅自離院　青山醫院報警","createTime":"2018-04-12T10:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T11:51:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3c23b749939b7b721c446f2193f23aae0ed96d","tid":626706,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"青山醫院今天(12日)公布一名住院男病人擅自離院。病房職員昨天(11日)下午約2時發現該名28歲男病人不知所終，隨即通知保安員全院搜索，惟未見蹤影。院方事後翻查閉路電視紀錄，相信有關病人已擅自離開醫院。<br />\n<br />\n根據閉路電視紀錄，病人離院時身穿黑色外套及深色長褲，身高約1.74米、中等身材、黑色頭髮及佩戴眼鏡。院方呼籲公眾人士如發現有關病人，請即致電： 62735787 通知警方新界北總區失蹤人口調查組或致電青山醫院熱線電話： 24567111 。<br />\n<br />\n院方已即時報警及通知病人家屬，該病人早前入住該院精神科病房，經治療後病情已有改善，正接受精神科康復治療；院方已向醫院管理局總辦事處呈報事件。"},{"pid":"8dfcce1aca3d57b6ea4caa4adcc247fe340c0a9c","tid":626706,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1313d4f7b9020fe9209fb49b638bec34dd4d5ee","tid":626706,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"會員青山走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82164e5ac210185e0379788f22a8dc3acd1ee46a","tid":626706,"uid":25822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"回魂夜Leo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0b6fea0caa0a937890a09c3a67c890bb6e7fc2","tid":626706,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"先生，請問你係咪青山走犯？"},{"pid":"93e22486de4fa9d5eafb16682039952adcd38a16","tid":626706,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"飛越瘋人院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18058fa7a39a71298c1b9915a58b4a7ff9962480","tid":626706,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"我冇痴